column5: Ryan,  After reading your thread, I was so happy that it was such a success that I wanted to do more.... more in given you a special gift.... cause you've accomplished / done so much for this worthy cause    and been such a great ambassador that today, got working on a project and just wanted to give you a sneak peek    I ain't telling what it is.... but you'll be the first to know when I put it in the mail  I'd like to take this opportunity to say thank you for just being you!!! I also think that a big round of applause is in order   :clapping:  :clapping:  :clapping:  :clapping:  Well done my friend and tight lines Jacques
This could morph into an OFC style rorschach test.  There's a lot of things that could be.
Ryan,  Tried to send you a PM but I think your mailbox is full  A little package is on it's way.... you should receive it next week  Tight lines Jacques
